sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Mind
    participant CX as Cortex
    participant RC as Recall
    participant HP as Hippocampus
    participant SY as Synapse

    C->>CX: reflect (criteria, scope)
    CX->>RC: ReflectQuery
    RC->>HP: Query candidates (by staleness, time span, weak associations)
    HP-->>RC: MemoryRetrieved (candidates for review)
    RC-->>CX: Reflection set (memories needing judgment)
    CX-->>C: Here are memories to review

    loop Mind reviews each memory
        C->>CX: associate_memories (A, B, type, strength)
        CX->>SY: AssociateCommand
        SY->>SY: Create/strengthen semantic association

        C->>CX: reclassify_memory (ID, new tier)
        CX->>HP: ReclassifyCommand
        HP->>HP: Move memory, update metadata
        HP-->>SY: MemoryReclassified
    end

    C->>CX: reflect complete
